    <h2>Strategic Divorce Representation Across Maryland</h2>
    <p>
      Divorce is one of the most significant legal transitions a person can face. At Child Custody with a Plan, we believe divorce shouldn't just be something you survive — it should be something you approach with a strategy. Our Maryland divorce attorneys bring the expertise, preparation, and advocacy necessary to achieve the best possible outcome for your unique situation.
